Credits to whoever on Rune server for renamed. I just renamed the renamed version, making it non-renamed. Anyways....

What this tutorial will do is get rid of the loading bar and just leave the text, you could also remove the text too and it's very easy to figure that out. SO

Find this in your client class.
[code]aClass15_1109.method237(0);[/code]


You should see a block of code similar to this
[code]aClass15_1109.method237(0);
char c = '\u0168';
char c1 = '\310';
byte byte1 = 20;
aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, "Loading -Please Wait.", 23693, c1 / 2 - 26 - byte1, c / 2);
int j = c1 / 2 - 18 - byte1;
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 152, 304, 34, 0x8c1111, j, true);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 151, 302, 32, 0, j + 1, true);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, c / 2 - 150, 0x8c1111, i * 3, 0);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, (c / 2 - 150) + i * 3, 0, 300 - i * 3, 0);
aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, s, 23693, (c1 / 2 + 5) - byte1, c / 2);
aClass15_1109.method238(171, 23680, super.aGraphics12, 202);[/code]


Now I'm going to break this down.

These lines tell the text where to print out.
[code]
char c = '\u0168';
char c1 = '\310';
[/code]

This line ,obviously, prints out the text
[code]aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, "Loading -Please Wait.", 23693, c1 / 2 - 26 - byte1, c / 2);[/code]

These five lines are what create the loading bar.
[code]
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 152, 304, 34, 0x8c1111, j, true);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 151, 302, 32, 0, j + 1, true);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, c / 2 - 150, 0x8c1111, i * 3, 0);
Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, (c / 2 - 150) + i * 3, 0, 300 - i * 3, 0);
aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, s, 23693, (c1 / 2 + 5) - byte1, c / 2);[/code]


To remove any of those things just simply comment out the lines you'd like to not have so for example.
[code]aClass15_1109.method237(0);
char c = '\u0168';
char c1 = '\310';
byte byte1 = 20;
aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, "Loading -Please Wait.", 23693, c1 / 2 - 26 - byte1, c / 2);
int j = c1 / 2 - 18 - byte1;
//Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 152, 304, 34, 0x8c1111, j, true);
//Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method337(c / 2 - 151, 302, 32, 0, j + 1, true);
//Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, c / 2 - 150, 0x8c1111, i * 3, 0);
//Class30_Sub2_Sub1.method336(30, j + 2, (c / 2 - 150) + i * 3, 0, 300 - i * 3, 0);
//aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_1272.method381(0xffffff, s, 23693, (c1 / 2 + 5) - byte1, c / 2);
aClass15_1109.method238(171, 23680, super.aGraphics12, 202);[/code]
This would be not having a loading bar.

That's all. Thanks ^^

